WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.690
My name is Nanfu.

00:00:03.365 --> 00:00:06.240
In Chinese, "nan" means "man."

00:00:06.952 --> 00:00:08.769
And "fu" means "pillar."

00:00:09.579 --> 00:00:11.692
My family had hoped for a boy,

00:00:11.716 --> 00:00:15.049
who would grow up
to be the pillar of the family.

00:00:15.692 --> 00:00:17.931
And when I turned out to be a girl,

00:00:17.955 --> 00:00:19.811
they named me Nanfu anyway.

00:00:19.835 --> 00:00:21.260
(Laughter)

00:00:21.284 --> 00:00:23.712
I was born in 1985,

00:00:23.736 --> 00:00:27.403
six years before China announced
its one-child policy.

00:00:28.958 --> 00:00:31.204
Right after I was born,